It's all bloody complicated and I need to study data science more.

In all likelihood, this board won't be any actual use, I suppose, moreso because I lost the user key for it and now I can't modify it, but if even just you took the time to poke through his work and determine for yourself if it holds merit, I feel it was worth it. I think Cultstate is a genius and I don't make that kind of statement lightly.
